snippet.textDisplay: Personally, I was actually hoping for a sword character, just not a Fire Emblem one.  I was really hoping Hollow Knight would get some representation with either the Knight or Hornet, since it’s a really good game and I don’t think a mii costume would do their move sets justice (also a mii costume wouldn’t get a map or multiple sound tracks into the game) and even if it wasn’t a Hollow Knight character , I would have preferred a franchise without representation in smash rather than one of the most represented.
